epresentation and adapters should v1 use?\",\"Which diff algorithms best suppress conversion noise?\",\"Which snapshot lifecycle is safe and predictable?\",\"How should the HTML report expose fidelity and risk?\",\"Which portable core and skill interface should v1 implement?\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"diff-match-patch library\",\"reason\":\"Repository archived Aug 2024; no maintenance\",\"evidence\":\"GitHub repo status\"},{\"approach\":\"Python runtime\",\"reason\":\"No diff2html equivalent; HTML rendering harder\",\"evidence\":\"npm ecosystem analysis\"},{\"approach\":\"Rust/WASM runtime\",\"reason\":\"Ecosystem mismatch\",\"evidence\":\"npm ecosystem analysis\"},{\"approach\":\"Deno runtime\",\"reason\":\"Smaller ecosystem\",\"evidence\":\"Runtime comparison\"},{\"approach\":\"SQLite snapshot storage\",\"reason\":\"Unnecessary dependency for v1\",\"evidence\":\"Storage strategy analysis\"},{\"approach\":\"PDF diff support in v1\",\"reason\":\"No parser preserves layout\",\"evidence\":\"Library ecosystem assessment\"},{\"approach\":\"Server-side rendering\",\"reason\":\"Violates local-first constraint\",\"evidence\":\"spec.md\"},{\"approach\":\"External CDN dependencies\",\"reason\":\"Violates self-contained requirement\",\"evidence\":\"spec.md\"},{\"approach\":\"Custom diff algorithm\",\"reason\":\"jsdiff is extensible enough\",\"evidence\":\"jsdiff API analysis\"},{\"approach\":\"GUI-only interface\",\"reason\":\"Violates AI agent integration requirement\",\"evidence\":\"spec.md\"},{\"approach\":\"REST API\",\"reason\":\"Violates local-only constraint\",\"evidence\":\"spec.md\"}],\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-13T15:22:00Z\",\"durationMs\":75000}\nJSONL","description":"Append JSONL deltas for iterations 4-10"},"output":"(no output)","metadata":{"output":"(no output)","exit":0,"truncated":false},"title":"cat >> /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/136-standalone-document-diff-skill/001-resear